headline: Is Regency Centers Attractively Priced After Recent Retail Leasing Momentum in 2025?
summary: If you are weighing what to do next with Regency Centers stock, you are in good company. The chatter around this retail-centered REIT has been getting livelier, and for good reason. While the market’s been wobbly in recent months, Regency Centers has kept its cool, dropping just 2.4% in the last week but eking out a small gain over the past month. Year-to-date numbers are only down 1.2%, and despite this mild pullback, the stock is still up nearly 37% over three years and a striking 134.7%...
